EN: Athletes should adhere to anti-doping regulations.

ZH: 这个国家对兴奋剂的使用非常严厉。
EN: This country has strict penalties for the use of performance-enhancing drugs.

ZH: 兴奋剂在竞技体育中被广泛使用。
EN: Performance-enhancing drugs are widely used in competitive sports.

